Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:04.67,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The exquisitely perfect temperature \Nof the water loosens my stiff muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.02,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The arm I hit when I tripped,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:10.12,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and the pain of my twisted ankle, \Nall melt away into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.23,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the velvety water seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.44,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,it'll make my skin nice and smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.14,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now this is true happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:17.99,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:21.12,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Slightly salty... It's a salt water spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.59,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Not only can you bathe in it, but I bet \Ndrinking it would be good for anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:28.38,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, you shouldn't drink it if you've \Ngot high blood pressure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.10,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.64,Main,LANDLADY,0,0,0,,Welcome. The end of the line is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.32,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A reporting job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:44.39,big breakthrough,TEXT,0,0,0,,An Idol's Report Gave It \NIts Big Break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.24,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Your spur-of-the-moment hot spring report
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.39,visiting the beautiful landlady's,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(1695,1)\c&H0000D8&}Visiting the {\c&Ha03bcb&}Beautiful Mistress's{\c&H0000d8&} \NSecret Hot Spring Inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.39,Main,AI,0,0,0,,that aired the other day was a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:45.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:49.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you, President Ai and Matsukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:51.87,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I was so tired then, and it was... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.40,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Is that what you call a tutti-frutti?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.30,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You mean a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.95,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,It felt so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.28,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You really hit, hit, hit home with the viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.96,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Since the broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:07.96,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,121,453 guests have flocked to that inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.21,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Is that a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:14.13,tottori,TEXT,0,0,0,,Tottori Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:14.13,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,It's roughly a fifth of the population of Tottori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:15.76,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.64,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,Let's Go! \N1,000 Famous Japanese Hot Springs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.64,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You're getting jobs for hot spring \Nreports one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.14,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:23.34,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A track suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.00,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You'll sprint to the hot spring \Nwhere you're shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:27.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:29.60,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,By getting exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:32.61,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,you'll be able to give a genuine \Nhot spring report again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.86,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's only 23 kilometers \Naway as the crow flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.91,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.88,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Kokona ran! You can do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.37,visiting the beautiful landlady's,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}Seeking Tenants
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.37,love pro,,0,0,0,,Hair Salon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:41.87,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.37,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.61,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Fight! Swing your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.67,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,So Komugi-chan ran, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.04,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She ran and ran until she was exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:57.13,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's as though my exhausted body is melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:59.09,towels,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\fad(190,1)\an1}*We are using towels due to filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Am I in heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:02.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Then she gave a report that felt very genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.63,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Go, go! Lift your thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:06.14,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Then she ran again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.47,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My soul might just leave my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:15.44,towels,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(190,1)}*We are using school swimsuits due to filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I feel as though I'm enveloped in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:15.44,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,And she gave lots of genuine-feeling reports, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.82,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Every program had great ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.32,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Could this finally be Komugi-chan's \Nbig break as an idol, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.29,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Hey, don't forgot about \Ncollecting Fan-C Cards, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.12,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,459)}Nurse Witch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.12,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(1,459)}Komugi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.12,Title3,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(1,459)}R
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.38,dorm mimosa,SIGN,0,0,0,,Nijigaoka Academy Student Dorm Mimosa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.99,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,So anyway, I've been working a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.51,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,That's great, Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.05,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's all so we can sing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.85,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,at the Tokyo Skydome together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.94,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to catch up to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.77,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:12.98,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It kind of makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.17,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Being popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's more like my reports are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,bringing lots of guests to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.43,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Does it make the guests and the people \Nwho run the hot springs happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Are they having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Um... I don't know how to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:32.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but it makes me happy to \Nbe able to help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.43,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's okay. You are helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Really? Good, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.33,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're both filming on location
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,with Yu-nii tomorrow and the day after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.76,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.56,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's for the movie {\i1}Jurassic: Impossible{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.60,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,We'll be back by evening \Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.76,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.56,Main,BOTH,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.07,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Today's shoot is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:02.99,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.82,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.42,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Go for under four!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.81,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,"Under four" refers to running a full \Nmarathon in under four hours, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.83,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,It's an amazing feat, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.89,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll do my best again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.08,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:19.00,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.00,downtown mall,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an2}Urabure Hot Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, it's really crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It seems like an old, gloomy hot spring \Nthat might collapse at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.23,Main,LANDLADY,0,0,0,,It has a ten-thousand-year history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.02,Main,LANDLADY,0,0,0,,But soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.56,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Since I'm exhausted from running so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm excited for the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:42.09,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan was tired, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.30,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She was exhausted from running \Nsuch long distances every day, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.79,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,So she tripped over nothing, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:51.26,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Tripping over nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.45,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,That sounds just like life, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I made a big mistake yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.33,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You can't change what's already done, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.28,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,No use crying over spilled milk, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.19,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.19,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I bet President Ai is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.97,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,K-Komuhellogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.70,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.94,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.66,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Komugi will be fired {\i1}(kubi){\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.45,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.33,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Yes, it's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.45,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Now Kokona will be Love Pro's only—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.96,downtown mall,SIGN,0,0,0,,Talent Production Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.96,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:42.96,next ep title - pink,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Komugi-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.55,downtown mall,SIGN,0,0,0,,Shitamachi Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.60,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,It sure is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.45,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,It's cold, and you're eating ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.30,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You're shivering, but feeling nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:58.76,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.69,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.72,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:02.15,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,What happened, yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.69,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.12,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I was fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.72,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.45,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,She was fired from Love Pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.82,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Her idol career is finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.69,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.45,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.45,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.12,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I was fired from Love Pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.27,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:23.13,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It must be because I ruined that hot spring inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.46,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,K-Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.47,yoshida clinic night,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an2}Yoshida Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.47,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,Well, of course they'd fire you if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.24,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Ch-Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.03,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My idol career is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.33,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.77,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,They say tears are the sweat of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.35,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.15,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Does this mean we won't get to \Nsee pharmacy concerts anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.37,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,We won't get to see Komugi-chan \Nplaying corpses on TV, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.74,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.91,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,No! I can't bear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.95,love pro,SIGN,0,0,0,,Love Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.28,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Please don't fire Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.67,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.63,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.54,Main,AI,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.52,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,So it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.31,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Please don't fire her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.05,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.55,Main,AI,0,0,0,,But it's already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.60,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about that? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.74,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.74,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Please lift your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.44,Main,AI,0,0,0,,I think being fired will be a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.91,Main,AI,0,0,0,,very good thing for Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.15,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,So she's fired, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.26,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.33,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Komugi is fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.12,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I'm back from—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.63,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.72,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.67,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.88,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Who knows? I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.15,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Shozo-san, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.38,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.33,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Since my old lady passed away before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.14,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,my only reasons to live have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.63,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,My granddaughter, drinking, \Nreading, travel, movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:05.41,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,ceramics, mixers, golf, fishing, photography,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.91,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,mountain climbing, sushi, tempura,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:11.86,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,social work, volunteer work, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.81,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan! That's all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:15.16,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.28,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,We all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.82,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,...love Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.99,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.12,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Her smiles always gave me energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.39,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,If Komugi-chan is feeling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.25,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,we should be helping her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.06,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.09,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.84,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan and Tsukasa-chan aren't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.43,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.23,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,I heard they had an on-location shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.97,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,Maybe you should ask the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.02,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.60,Main,WOMAN,0,0,0,,She seems unusually down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.66,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better that they weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.03,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What should I tell Kokona-chan and Tsukasa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:59.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That we can't keep our promise \Nto sing together anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.01,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You brought it on yourself, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You could at least try to cheer me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.37,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Now, now. It's all about perspective, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.79,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Now you can focus on collecting Fan-C Cards, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.46,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Now you can work for me only, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.31,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that, pyon! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.47,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Ow, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.42,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, I said that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.23,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.60,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Cheer up, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.46,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Come on, scream into the sunset, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.54,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Doesn't your heart want to scream, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.33,Main - Italics,AI,0,0,0,,Komugi will be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:38.60,Main - Italics,MATSU,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.42,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,President Ai and Matsukawa-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,seem to be happier without me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.04,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,The normally optimistic Komugi-chan \Nis seriously depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.10,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,This is a serious— Pyon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.54,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.16,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, my ears are \Nstanding at attention, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.82,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There's a monster nearby, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:57.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.44,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Yeah, a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:03.05,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You can take out your sadness over the \Nend of your idol career on a monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.22,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Take out my sadness on a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.59,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,That's right, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Take out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,my sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.15,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,on a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.87,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Parasol shiny chloroform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:22.72,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Chanting it deciphers the code\Nprogrammed into the incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.49,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shiny lovely tenipole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.16,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It scans Komugi's entire body while
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.90,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,simultaneously sending the \Ndata to the Fanta-C World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:30.26,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,It's instantly analyzed, and \NChan-G rays are fired at Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.46,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The rays turn Komugi's caring heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.55,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,into Amazoni-N Cells, activating \Ntheir maximum Tombo-E potential
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:41.11,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,and reconstructing her body and costume,\Ncompleting the Chan-G.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.68,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,On average, the transformation\Ntakes 0.02 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:48.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Monster, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.10,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.50,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,Sleep, sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.87,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,Yawning monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.21,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.71,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,What was that for, yawn {\i1}(akubi){\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:17.84,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kubi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Even monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.84,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Even monsters are making fun of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.93,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, yawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.26,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Don't say "{\i1}kubi{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.28,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Go, pyon! Go get him, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.89,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.73,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.77,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,M-Maybe you should
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:46.74,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,finish it off with one of your \Nspecial moves now, pyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Nurse Dumb-Dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Stabby Blooming Riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.90,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Kan-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.97,Main,YAWN,0,0,0,,Yawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.47,yawning doll,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2\fad(317,1)}Yawning Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.80,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,We got the Fan-C Card, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.23,downtown mall,,0,0,0,,Yawning \NDoll \NMonster
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.73,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.28,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Take that! Take that! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.88,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,She's scary, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.57,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Don't say "yawn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.28,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Was being fired from her idol \Nwork that big a shock, pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.98,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Damn you, damn you, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Usa-P, you might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:25.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Since I was fired from Love Pro, \NI can't keep being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:33.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Maybe all I have left is being the Magical Nurse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and beating up monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.00,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I guess I'm done being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.26,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,There you are, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.26,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.91,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.01,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:50.92,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:51.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.02,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Just come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.23,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Guys, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.11,you can do it our idol,SIGN,0,0,0,,You can do it! Our idol Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.11,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Ta-da, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,This is just like the stage I dreamed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.83,you can do it our idol,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20}You can do it! Our idol Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.83,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,Everyone in the shopping district made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.46,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.08,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Shozo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.87,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,We all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.15,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,worked together to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.91,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.93,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? But I was fired from Love Pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.93,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,We want you to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But I'm not an idol anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.96,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}our{\i0} idol, Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.73,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Even if you've been fired from Love Pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.03,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You're still an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.49,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.49,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,We all love you, Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:53.15,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,We love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.05,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,You mustn't abandon your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.33,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.85,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,An idol's mission is to make \Ntheir fans' dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:02.84,Main,FRIEND,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.39,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Yeah. Are you going to abandon your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.51,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You may have been fired from Love Pro, \Nbut you haven't lost your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.72,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.94,Main,TOMOYA,0,0,0,,Komugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.14,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Everyone supports you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.39,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,You're an idol, aren't you? Then sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:21.90,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi! Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.47,Main - Top,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi! Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.58,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,That's right, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.71,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Having you be not just a \NTombo-E Girl, but also an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.71,Main - Top,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi! Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.88,Main - Top,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi! Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.99,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,wasn't so bad, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.07,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,And you're less scary when \Nyou're working as an idol, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.51,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Usa-P...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.38,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.15,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shozo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.05,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Let's Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.06,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugication!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:27.09,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Your rays of sunlight are \Ngiving me love heartburn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:32.17,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,It's giving me an off-season heatstroke
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:37.93,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,You're always honest and too hard-working
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:42.77,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,I can't help but want to support you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:48.27,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,When you're tired and things get rough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.15,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,You can
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.61,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah... I finally get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:55.26,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,call my name anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.26,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I started working as an idol on a whim,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.49,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.60,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but having people who support me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:01.66,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,I'll run to your side anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.67,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:06.98,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,I'll hear your voice sending a call of love
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.15,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.44,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,You think I did well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:12.38,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,On angel wings, your energy will rise and go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.78,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.09,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I make other people happy,\Neven if only a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:17.09,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,You'll feel energy well up inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.68,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and help them have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.84,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And I'm also cheered up and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:22.97,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,So always remember
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.73,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,receive support from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.97,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,These are wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.44,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,Mugi Mugi in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:27.87,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, as long \Nas I have fans, I'll be an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:30.15,Main - Top - Italics,SONG,0,0,0,,The magic that connects hearts to hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:31.04,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll never say I'll quit being an idol again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:35.65,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I realized this because \NI was fired from Love Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.69,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now {\i0}this{\i1} must be a tutti-frutti!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.41,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Good work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.17,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You have tomorrow off, so get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:49.27,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:52.17,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving us a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.61,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.12,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You were heading back to \Nthe same dorm anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.51,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Bitter enemies in the same boat,\Nsharing the same fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.52,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.44,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.10,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.64,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.04,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What event was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.49,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,"Komugi-chan Concert"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.97,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Was this one of her jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.44,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, President Ai! Matsukawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan, Tsukasa-kun, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,President Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.96,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.91,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,to keep being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.17,Main,AI,0,0,0,,What do you mean, keep being an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Even if I'm fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:35.67,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.68,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.27,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.43,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.18,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Komugi, you knew about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:46.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sorry. I overheard you talking in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.14,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:51.56,Main,AI,0,0,0,,I was going to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.84,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.19,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.46,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You've been fired {\i1}(kubi){\i0}. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.03,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Um... President Ai, Matsukawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:05.74,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.40,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we hadn't told you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.04,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You know that the popular card game
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.04,Main,AI,0,0,0,,"Buri Bara" is going to be \Nmade into an anime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.26,Main - Top,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah. I auditioned for it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.26,buri bara anime,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}The popular card game \NBuri Bara is getting animated!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:19.10,Main,TSUKSA,0,0,0,,Yuto's going to be playing Skirt Steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.10,Main,STEAK,0,0,0,,Skirt Steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.26,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I'm Tachibana Yuto. I'll be playing Skirt Steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.26,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}Skirt Steak (Beef)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.26,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}CV: Yachibana Yuto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.80,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Yeah, and Kokona is going to be Short Rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.80,Main - Top,KALBI,0,0,0,,Short Rib.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.52,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}Short Rib (Beef)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.52,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}CV: Saionji Kokona
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.52,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.22,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.77,Main,AI,0,0,0,,And Komugi got a role, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.06,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You're playing Neck {\i1}(kubi){\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What? Neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.99,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Didn't you audition for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.27,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.66,Main,NECK,0,0,0,,Neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.99,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}Neck (Beef)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.99,downtown mall,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an2}CV: Yoshida Komugi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.78,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Neck is a supporting role \Ninstead of a regular one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.60,Main,AI,0,0,0,,but it has quite a bit of screen time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.02,Main,AI,0,0,0,,and your hot spring reports \Nhave been popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.57,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Kokona won't be Love Pro's only primary idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.50,Main,AI,0,0,0,,You'll be one too, Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.12,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Then when you "{\i1}kubi{\i0},"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.01,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,you didn't mean I was fired from Love Pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.47,Main,AI,0,0,0,,No, I meant "{\i1}kubi{\i0}" as in Neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.79,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's great, Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.68,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Way to go! Congratulations, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.97,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You earned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.10,Main,KOTARO,0,0,0,,What, you just jumped to \Nconclusions, you klutz?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.10,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Sounds like Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.65,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.12,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.11,Main,MAN,0,0,0,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But I ruined a hot spring inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Who's going to pay for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:27.12,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Oh, that inn was already scheduled \Nto be torn down soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:32.37,manju,,0,0,0,,{\fad(501,1)}Urabure Manju
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.44,Main,AI,0,0,0,,The owner sent us a box of sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.37,Main,AI,0,0,0,,to thank us for saving her the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.63,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,R-Really? Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.68,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You've got another hot spring \Nreport tomorrow, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.13,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,You'll be running to Hakone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,O-Okay! Komu-got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:49.26,Main,AI,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you explain this situation for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.67,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.63,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.43,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm Yoshida Komugi, age 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:29.53,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sagittarius, blood type O.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:32.53,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm an ordinary second-year \Nmiddle school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:35.04,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,but I'll be an idol forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:44.51,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:36.57,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Matsukawa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:38.71,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,When I see signs telling \Nme to park facing forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.69,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,in the parking lot, it makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:44.51,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I call forward-facing parking \N"positive parking."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:46.86,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,The next episode is \N"Tsukasa's Miracle White Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:50.05,next ep title,TEXT,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's \NMiracle White Day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:49.73,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,Never give up!